">Loi sur la cession du droit au remboursement en matière d’impôt</XRefExternal> doit être conforme à l’annexe II.</Text><HistoricalNote><HistoricalNoteSubItem lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="878438" lims:id="878438">DORS/92-509, art. 1</HistoricalNoteSubItem></HistoricalNote></Section></Body><Schedule lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:lastAmendedDate="2006-03-22" lims:fid="878439" lims:id="878439" bilingual="no" spanlanguages="no"><ScheduleFormHeading lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="878440" lims:id="878440"><Label>ANNEXE I</Label><OriginatingRef>(article 2)</OriginatingRef></ScheduleFormHeading><Provision lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="878441" lims:id="878441" format-ref="indent-0-0" language-align="no" list-item="no"><Text>CE GRAPHIQUE N’EST PAS EXPOSÉ, VOIR DORS/96-405, ART. 1</Text></Provision><HistoricalNote><HistoricalNoteSubItem lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="878443" lims:id="878443">DORS/92-509, art. 2; DORS/94-190, art. 1; DORS/96-405, art. 1</HistoricalNoteSubItem></HistoricalNote></Schedule><Schedule lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:lastAmendedDate="2006-03-22" lims:fid="878444" lims:id="878444" bilingual="no" spanlanguages="no"><ScheduleFormHeading lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="878445" lims:id="878445"><Label>ANNEXE II</Label><OriginatingRef>(article 3)</OriginatingRef></ScheduleFormHeading><Provision lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="878446" lims:id="878446" format-ref="indent-0-0" language-align="no" list-item="no"><Text>CE GRAPHIQUE N’EST PAS EXPOSÉ, VOIR DORS/96-405, ART. 1</Text></Provision><HistoricalNote><HistoricalNoteSubItem lims:inforce-start-date="2006-03-22" lims:fid="878448" lims:id="878448">DORS/92-509, art. 2; DORS/96-405, art. 1</HistoricalNoteSubItem></HistoricalNote></Schedule></Regulation>